Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "url",
  "title": "Test Bookmark"
}


### Test: Create Bookmark with Invalid URL
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/bookmarks
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "not-a-valid-url",
  "category": "url"
}


